1
00:00:00,326 --> 00:00:04,850
♪A little bit sorry for my love for you♪

2
00:00:04,850 --> 00:00:10,354
♪Sorry, I was a little late♪

3
00:00:10,354 --> 00:00:16,782
♪I really want the unconscious longing
to appear faster♪

4
00:00:16,782 --> 00:00:21,262
♪Can I get closer
and hear you say "I do" once more♪

5
00:00:21,262 --> 00:00:25,710
♪Holding hands, the scenery
in midsummer is a new journey♪

6
00:00:25,710 --> 00:00:30,621
♪The chapters of a fairy tale
are performed one after another♪

7
00:00:30,621 --> 00:00:34,670
♪The promised moment
will definitely not be forgotten♪

8
00:00:34,670 --> 00:00:39,205
♪Can I get closer and listen to
the frequency of your heartbeat♪

9
00:00:39,205 --> 00:00:43,502
♪Start the countdown 4321,
a new scenery♪

10
00:00:43,502 --> 00:00:48,267
♪I want to see all the scenes about you♪

11
00:00:48,267 --> 00:00:51,758
♪No need to miss you anymore♪

12
00:00:51,758 --> 00:00:55,438
♪Right by your side♪

13
00:00:57,084 --> 00:01:00,462
=Jin Secretary=

14
00:01:00,462 --> 00:01:03,150
=Episode 11=

15
00:01:04,266 --> 00:01:06,766
Okay, I promise you.

16
00:01:15,133 --> 00:01:18,699
Deal.

17
00:01:18,833 --> 00:01:22,199
Ahem, deal.

18
00:01:27,166 --> 00:01:28,300
Deal.

19
00:01:37,400 --> 00:01:40,533
(Mr. Lan's condition
seems to have improved a bit.)

20
00:01:40,533 --> 00:01:45,033
(But being by his side, I can feel
the heavy burden and pressure on him.)

21
00:01:46,066 --> 00:01:50,199
(For my sister's sake,
I still hope to help him.)

22
00:02:04,100 --> 00:02:07,500
Miss Jin, sort out all the bills
from the past three years.

23
00:02:07,566 --> 00:02:09,799
There's quite a lot of data.
I'll have Yuan help.

24
00:02:09,799 --> 00:02:10,733
Okay.

25
00:02:15,533 --> 00:02:16,433
Mr. Lan.

26
00:02:17,700 --> 00:02:18,500
Sit down.

27
00:02:22,666 --> 00:02:26,066
Mr. Lan, every single bill
and transaction of our group

28
00:02:26,066 --> 00:02:28,000
is synchronized and uploaded
to our finance system.

29
00:02:28,466 --> 00:02:31,333
And this system is currently
of the highest level of security.

30
00:02:31,866 --> 00:02:34,066
Is the one managing this system
a human or a computer?

31
00:02:39,400 --> 00:02:40,300
A human.

32
00:02:48,266 --> 00:02:49,900
Excuse me. I have to take this.

33
00:02:55,166 --> 00:02:56,699
- Hi.
- Hello, sis.

34
00:02:57,000 --> 00:02:58,266
I just thought about it.

35
00:02:58,433 --> 00:03:01,500
The project leader, Liang Liangqiang,
and the admin director, Bu Zhengjing

36
00:03:01,533 --> 00:03:03,566
often gave me some strange tasks.

37
00:03:11,533 --> 00:03:13,733
Hand it over to us by tomorrow morning.
Did you hear me?

38
00:03:13,933 --> 00:03:15,066
Don't slack off.

39
00:03:15,666 --> 00:03:18,466
Hey, the flowers are not bad.
Take them to Liang Liangqiang.

40
00:03:18,466 --> 00:03:19,133
Let's go.

41
00:03:28,166 --> 00:03:30,900
There was a strange financial report.

42
00:03:31,366 --> 00:03:32,600
I was curious and took a look.

43
00:03:32,733 --> 00:03:36,466
The data was significantly different
from the company's income.

44
00:03:45,133 --> 00:03:48,099
Tell me, where are Mei Xiangfa
and Zuo Jiazhang?

45
00:03:48,300 --> 00:03:49,766
How would I know?

46
00:03:51,066 --> 00:03:52,799
What do you want from them?

47
00:03:53,566 --> 00:03:55,799
Four months ago,
you gave me a financial statement.

48
00:03:55,833 --> 00:03:59,433
The data didn't mesh with the income
and expenditure. What's going on?

49
00:03:59,833 --> 00:04:02,333
How can I remember something
from four months ago?

50
00:04:02,433 --> 00:04:04,466
And what does it have to do with them?

51
00:04:07,233 --> 00:04:08,300
You won't say, huh?

52
00:04:08,400 --> 00:04:10,400
Liang Liangqiang told me.
Where are they?

53
00:04:11,699 --> 00:04:13,499
They're at the Guodan Club.

54
00:04:22,533 --> 00:04:23,199
Sis.

55
00:04:23,200 --> 00:04:26,733
It's not clear yet. Don't act rashly.

56
00:04:26,866 --> 00:04:27,666
Don't worry.

57
00:04:28,166 --> 00:04:31,200
The world is different from your arena.

58
00:04:32,133 --> 00:04:34,700
Silly girl, I understand.

59
00:04:45,633 --> 00:04:49,100
Look, my hand is swollen
and my nails are broken.

60
00:04:49,166 --> 00:04:52,333
Gosh, why do you tell her everything?

61
00:04:52,433 --> 00:04:55,199
If you're not afraid,
why don't you go fight with her?

62
00:04:56,633 --> 00:04:57,966
It hurts so much.

63
00:05:02,200 --> 00:05:03,566
- Mr. Li.
- Mr. Li.

64
00:05:03,866 --> 00:05:05,099
What's going on?

65
00:05:07,333 --> 00:05:09,833
Come on, let's drink.

66
00:05:10,600 --> 00:05:15,966
With that liability system, we have to
work overtime. Can't even pass the buck.

67
00:05:16,566 --> 00:05:20,933
Finally, we can relax.
Today, let me show you a unique skill.

68
00:05:21,833 --> 00:05:23,333
I'll bottom it up.

69
00:05:23,333 --> 00:05:23,733
Oh, my.

70
00:05:23,733 --> 00:05:26,399
That's not appropriate.
Here, take this. Come on.

71
00:05:26,433 --> 00:05:27,499
Wait a minute.

72
00:05:27,866 --> 00:05:29,000
Let me tell you something serious.

73
00:05:32,133 --> 00:05:33,366
Have you heard?

74
00:05:33,366 --> 00:05:34,233
What?

75
00:05:34,900 --> 00:05:37,566
Lan Chen is investigating
the company's accounts.

76
00:05:39,066 --> 00:05:41,533
He is checking the accounts now?

77
00:05:41,633 --> 00:05:44,000
Haha. What was he doing before?

78
00:05:44,833 --> 00:05:47,900
That's it? The national and global,

79
00:05:48,033 --> 00:05:50,533
world-class financial expert?

80
00:05:52,066 --> 00:05:54,833
He really treats me, Zuo Jiazhang, as a false name.
[*Zuo Jiazhang as pinyin means "to cook the books"]

81
00:05:54,833 --> 00:05:55,500
Indeed.

82
00:05:55,566 --> 00:05:57,766
He even found Mr. Li
and that secretary, Miss Jin.

83
00:05:58,600 --> 00:06:01,100
- Found Mr. Li? Miss Jin?
- Yeah.

84
00:06:03,233 --> 00:06:06,333
If he can find out anything,
I'll take his last name.

85
00:06:09,833 --> 00:06:12,666
Are the accounts of WE Beauty Group
messed up by you guys?

86
00:06:12,666 --> 00:06:13,966
Wait, who are you? Why should I...

87
00:06:14,466 --> 00:06:15,599
Hey! What are you doing?

88
00:06:17,500 --> 00:06:19,166
Hey, I'll talk.

89
00:06:19,366 --> 00:06:21,899
I-I-I did mess with the accounts.

90
00:06:22,000 --> 00:06:23,300
But we were also instructed by someone.

91
00:06:23,333 --> 00:06:24,499
Who?

92
00:06:24,566 --> 00:06:25,400
It's Lan Chen.

93
00:06:25,666 --> 00:06:26,633
L-Lan Chen.

94
00:06:27,633 --> 00:06:28,666
L-Lan Chen.

95
00:06:28,833 --> 00:06:31,466
Yes, it's Lan Chen.
Lan Chen instructed us.

96
00:06:31,866 --> 00:06:32,933
Why aren't the reports public?

97
00:06:32,933 --> 00:06:35,099
Why haven't the accounts been published
for three years?

98
00:06:35,133 --> 00:06:37,666
Are you trying to deceive
Lihuai Group's investment?

99
00:06:41,133 --> 00:06:43,799
It's Lan Chen. Lan Chen instructed us.
Everything was instructed by Lan Chen.

100
00:06:43,800 --> 00:06:45,833
The current financial situation
of the Lan family has serious problems.

101
00:06:45,833 --> 00:06:49,299
He instructed us to falsify the accounts
to pass the quarterly assessment.

102
00:06:49,466 --> 00:06:52,666
That's right. He instructed us.
It was Lan Chen who instructed us.

103
00:07:04,710 --> 00:07:09,232
♪I pass through the crowd with you♪

104
00:07:12,262 --> 00:07:17,223
♪As if we have a tacit understanding,
attracting each other♪

105
00:07:20,272 --> 00:07:26,096
♪When the loneliness cracks,
warmth seeps in♪

106
00:07:26,096 --> 00:07:33,566
♪You come with light,
shining into my heart♪

107
00:07:33,566 --> 00:07:37,047
♪Stars fall into my eyes,
and you fall into my heart♪

108
00:07:37,047 --> 00:07:41,168
♪I make a wish foolishly,
but actually, you are the shooting star♪

109
00:07:41,168 --> 00:07:42,864
♪Open my secret♪

110
00:07:42,864 --> 00:07:48,912
♪I hope you find
all the tenderness hidden for you♪

111
00:07:48,912 --> 00:07:52,784
♪Sinking into your love,
I want to sink deeper♪

112
00:07:52,784 --> 00:07:57,290
♪With each breath,
I can feel the sweetness♪

113
00:07:57,290 --> 00:08:06,000
♪Two lonely islands meet,
and it's the gift of fate♪
